summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting three easements for sanitary sewer over portions of the Northwest Quarter of Section 28, township 24 North, Range 4 East, W.M., Corgiat Addition, and vacated South Warsaw Street, as part of the Sewer Outreach Phase IV program (South Corgiat Drive; RW 8816-3, RW 8816-4 and RW 8816-5).
